    "anchor_id": "testing-file",
    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/testing/#testing-file",
    "section_text": "Then you could have a file test_main.py with your tests. It could live on the same Python package (the same directory with a __init__.py file):\n\nBecause this file is in the same package, you can use relative imports to import the object app from the main module ( main.py ):\n\n...and have the code for the tests just like before.",
    "section_inline_code": [
